quick, son.

12:08.568 --> 12:10.448
And then send these niggas
on their way, a'ight?

12:11.772 --> 12:13.772
Man, listen.

12:13.774 --> 12:17.108
We one of Dmitri's top corners
'cause we keep shit moving.

12:17.110 --> 12:18.376
A'ight.

12:18.378 --> 12:19.711
Let's go, man.

12:19.713 --> 12:21.214
<font face="Rockwell">FRED:</font> Isaiah.

12:22.515 --> 12:24.752
Your sister know you here?

12:27.186 --> 12:28.822
You're better than this, son.

12:33.527 --> 12:35.663
Come by the shop,
you want a job.

12:40.868 --> 12:42.634
<font face="Rockwell">(SCREAMS)</font>

12:42.636 --> 12:44.336
- <font face="Rockwell">(LAUGHING)</font>
- The fuck you doing, man?

12:44.338 --> 12:46.171
You got a customer.

12:46.173 --> 12:47.372
The customer.

12:47.374 --> 12:48.507
The-the one and only.
<font face="Rockwell">(CHUCKLES)</font>

12:48.509 --> 12:49.543
What you need, Skeletor?

12:50.711 --> 12:53.680
Mmm, yeah, I smell your sweat.

12:53.682 --> 12:55.348
Innocent Isaiah just...

12:55.350 --> 12:57.249
<font face="Rockwell">(INHALES DEEPLY)</font>
fresh-fresh.

12:57.251 --> 12:58.585
What the fuck
you talking about, nigga?

12:58.587 --> 12:59.852
Ah, you green.

12:59.854 --> 13:02.387
Our first transaction's
on you, hmm?

13:02.389 --> 13:05.658
A little initiation fee
to get my biz

13:05.660 --> 13:07.860
with your fine-ass sister.

13:07.862 --> 13:10.663
Hey, yo, fuck you, fiend.
Move on.

13:10.665 --> 13:12.801
Get the fuck out
of my face, man.

13:15.604 --> 13:18.438
A blood baptism for Innocent I.

13:18.440 --> 13:19.907
<font face="Rockwell">(CHUCKLING)</font> Sure enough.

13:19.909 --> 13:22.508
See, that's what
the doctor ordered.

13:22.510 --> 13:26.679
And I'm the practicing
practitioner!

13:26.681 --> 13:28.348
- <font face="Rockwell">(ISAIAH YELLS)</font>
- <font face="Rockwell">(SKELETOR LAUGHING)</font>

13:28.350 --> 13:30.151
Yo, hold up, hold up.

13:33.221 --> 13:34.220
<font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font>
Yo, yo! Yo, we out!

13:34.222 --> 13:36.222
Hey, yo, clear out, yo!

13:36.224 --> 13:37.725
Hey, yo, come on, Isaiah.
Come on.

13:37.727 --> 13:38.959
- Come on.
- He cut me, man.

13:38.961 --> 13:41.562
For real?

13:41.564 --> 13:44.732
<font face="Rockwell">DMITRI:</font> I called y'all here
to discuss this experiment.

13:44.734 --> 13:47.401
I don't give a shit what other
people do during Purge night.

13:47.403 --> 13:49.637
I care about what you all do.

13:49.639 --> 13:53.507
You get hurt or you die,
I lose money.

13:53.509 --> 13:55.976
- And I don't lose money.
- Word. Word.

13:55.978 --> 13:58.680
- And we got enemies, right?
- Yeah, true.

13:58.682 --> 14:00.915
Niggas might use the night
to make a move on us.

14:00.917 --> 14:03.517
Maybe the police
might use the night

14:03.519 --> 14:04.919
to take out motherfuckers
like us.

14:04.921 --> 14:06.520
Who knows?

14:06.522 --> 14:09.623
Point is, we gotta
be prepared for anything.

14:09.625 --> 14:11.792
So we lay low.

14:11.794 --> 14:14.261
We stay inside, and we protect

14:14.263 --> 14:15.964
- what needs protecting.
- Word. - That's what's up.

14:15.966 --> 14:19.667
Our kin, our skin,

14:19.669 --> 14:22.837
our product and our money.

14:22.839 --> 14:24.639
Yo, D. We should all
just go to Brooklyn.

14:24.641 --> 14:26.608
You know what I mean?
So we don't even take a chance.

14:26.610 --> 14:29.411
Nah.
Nah, we can't move our money

14:29.413 --> 14:31.379
or our stash off the island.
It's too risky.

14:31.381 --> 14:34.949
- And it'll make us look weak.
- Come on, my G.

14:34.951 --> 14:37.986
This is bullshit.
I want to fucking purge, man.

14:37.988 --> 14:40.422
I want to tear shit up
and have some fucking fun.

14:40.424 --> 14:41.956
<font face="Rockwell">(CHUCKLES)</font>
For the first time in my life,

14:41.958 --> 14:43.391
I could be
a law-abiding citizen.

14:43.393 --> 14:44.796
- <font face="Rockwell">(LAUGHS)</font>
- <font face="Rockwell">(OTHERS MURMURING)</font>

14:47.397 --> 14:48.898
<font face="Rockwell">(GRUNTING)</font>

14:48.900 --> 14:50.598
<font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font> Oh!

14:50.600 --> 14:52.536
<font face="Rockwell">(WHEEZING)</font>

14:57.809 --> 15:00.009
If you so much as blink,

15:00.011 --> 15:03.845
Blaise will remove the skin
from your face, fat man.

15:03.847 --> 15:05.681
She does exactly what I say.

15:05.683 --> 15:07.285
You know why?

15:08.386 --> 15:09.985
We're family.

15:09.987 --> 15:11.821
I put food on her table,

15:11.823 --> 15:13.789
and I put money in her pocket.

15:13.791 --> 15:16.392
My only question for you is:

15:16.394 --> 15:18.461
I put food on your table.

15:18.463 --> 15:20.563
Why don't I get the same type
of discipline

15:20.565 --> 15:21.997
from your big ass?

15:21.999 --> 15:23.999
My bad, D.

15:24.001 --> 15:25.704
I'll stay home.

15:29.307 --> 15:30.307
Good boy.

15:32.778 --> 15:34.611
<font face="Rockwell">DMITRI:</font> Let's get through
this Purge bullshit

15:34.613 --> 15:37.013
so we can get back
to business as usual.

15:37.015 --> 15:39.350
<font face="Rockwell">(CELL PHONE BUZZING)</font>

15:41.720 --> 15:43.486
D.

15:43.488 --> 15:45.588
There's been an incident.

15:45.590 --> 15:48.793
- <font face="Rockwell">(WATER RUNNING)</font>
- Isaiah, man.

15:48.795 --> 15:51.695
- What you thinking?
- <font face="Rockwell">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

15:51.697 --> 15:54.966
- <font face="Rockwell">(SIGHS)</font>
- <font face="Rockwell">NYA:</font> Isaiah, you home?

15:54.968 --> 15:57.969
Yeah. I'm just showering, sis.

15:57.971 --> 16:00.437
Did you hear what happened
at Fourth and...

16:00.439 --> 16:02.073
Isaiah, what's going on?

16:02.075 --> 16:03.774
Why's there blood on the floor?
Are you good?

16:03.776 --> 16:05.809
- <font face="Rockwell">(DOOR RATTLING)</font>
- Yeah, I-I cut myself shaving.

16:05.811 --> 16:07.711
You need facial hair
in order to shave, boy.

16:07.713 --> 16:09.647
Open up the door,
or I'll kick it in.

16:09.649 --> 16:11.518
- You know I will.
- <font face="Rockwell">(DOOR RATTLING)</font>

16:12.352 --> 16:13.620
A'ight.

16:15.488 --> 16:17.588
Jesus Christ,
what happened to your neck?

16:17.590 --> 16:18.890
<font face="Rockwell">(ISAIAH SIGHS)</font>

16:18.892 --> 16:20.424
<font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font>
Keep your left up.

16:20.426 --> 16:22.929
Jab, jab, jab.

16:24.697 --> 16:26.564
Get it out, get it out!

16:26.566 --> 16:27.865
There you go.

16:27.867 --> 16:29.466
Hey, hey!

16:29.468 --> 16:30.668
<font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font>
It's all locked and loaded.

16:30.670 --> 16:32.137
We're gonna have
at least 20 soldiers

16:32.139 --> 16:33.705
surrounding this place,

16:33.707 --> 16:35.640
keeping it secure
during the experiment.

16:35.642 --> 16:37.675
Me and Blaise
will be at the stash house

16:37.677 --> 16:39.544
with about two dozen niggas
on the perimeter.

16:39.546 --> 16:40.613
We'll be protected.

16:44.384 --> 16:45.585
<font face="Rockwell">PLAYERS:</font> Oh!

16:47.154 --> 16:48.987
The eyes, Terence!

16:48.989 --> 16:50.454
The eyes, the eyes.

16:50.456 --> 16:52.057
Your eyes went right to Aesop.

16:52.059 --> 16:54.059
Now, me, you, everybody know
you tossing to Sop.

16:54.061 --> 16:56.695
You ain't talking, but you
telling me everything, man.

16:56.697 --> 16:57.930
Let's pay attention to that.

16:57.932 --> 16:59.097
Everything else
is good money, a'ight?

16:59.099 --> 17:00.399
Let's keep up the pace,
a'ight, boys?

17:00.401 --> 17:01.301
Whoa, what are you doing?

17:01.303 --> 17:02.302
- Thanks, D. Appreciate it.
- Of course.

17:02.304 --> 17:04.069
- Run it from the top.
- <font face="Rockwell">NYA:</font> Let me through!

17:04.070 --> 17:06.405
Let me through!
Get your hands off of me!

17:06.406 --> 17:07.772
- Don't touch me.
- Yo.

17:07.775 --> 17:09.540
Put your hands on me
one more time,

17:09.542 --> 17:11.143
I'll rip your fucking
balls off. Believe that.

17:11.145 --> 17:13.145
<font face="Rockwell">PLAYERS:</font> Ooh.

17:13.146 --> 17:14.814
To what do I owe this...

17:14.816 --> 17:17.652
Cut the shit.
I need to talk to you now.

17:20.021 --> 17:21.420
My office.

17:21.422 --> 17:25.090
<font face="Rockwell"> <i>♫ Motherfuckin' joke ♫</i> </font>

17:25.093 --> 17:31.463
<font face="Rockwell"> <i>♫ Steph Wes stay with
the fuckin' pole ♫</i> </font>

17:31.465 --> 17:34.466
<font face="Rockwell"> <i>♫ You fuck around ♫</i> </font>

17:34.468 --> 17:37.004
- <font face="Rockwell"> <i>♫ And get poled... ♫</i> </font>
- <font face="Rockwell">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

17:37.006 --> 17:38.438
You son of a...

17:38.440 --> 17:40.007
- Yo, yo, yo.
- I don't believe you.

17:40.009 --> 17:41.108
What is it? What's up?

17:41.110 --> 17:42.442
Isaiah was just cut

17:42.444 --> 17:44.611
by some junkie
off one of your corners.

17:44.613 --> 17:47.214
- What? Is he all right?
- He's going to be fine.

17:47.216 --> 17:48.848
He didn't want to go
to the hospital,

17:48.850 --> 17:50.750
'cause he was too afraid
I was going to find out

17:50.752 --> 17:52.051
he's been hooking school,

17:52.053 --> 17:53.586
working the corner
for the past week.

17:53.588 --> 17:55.121
I had no idea
he was involved, Nya.

17:55.123 --> 17:56.522
- Oh, bullshit.
- You think I know

17:56.524 --> 17:58.659
who works my corners?
Nya, come on. Nya.

17:58.661 --> 18:01.729
I would never let Isaiah get
anywhere close to the business.

18:01.731 --> 18:02.796
You know that.

18:02.798 --> 18:04.834
I watched that boy grow up.

18:06.936 --> 18:08.468
Why'd he... why'd he do it?

18:08.470 --> 18:09.569
Why else?

18:09.571 --> 18:11.005
He's sick of struggling.

18:11.007 --> 18:12.740
He wanted to make life
a little bit easier for us

18:12.742 --> 18:14.141
- with some extra cash.
- And I told you I would

18:14.143 --> 18:15.708
- give you money for that.
- Stop.

18:15.710 --> 18:17.644
I'll never take
your blood money.

18:17.646 --> 18:18.713
You know that.

18:19.815 --> 18:21.082
I-I tried talking to him.

18:21.084 --> 18:23.051
I tried...
I tried being his mother,

18:23.053 --> 18:25.519
his father, his brother,
his sister, but clearly,

18:25.521 --> 18:27.088
- I'm not doing a good enough job.
- Nya, Nya, hey.

18:27.090 --> 18:28.722
- Clearly, I can be...
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.

18:28.724 --> 18:30.826
It's a'ight. I got you.

18:33.930 --> 18:36.166
I want you to stay with me
during the Purge, a'ight?

18:38.100 --> 18:40.169
You and Isaiah.

18:41.604 --> 18:43.171
As far as that...

18:43.173 --> 18:45.707
as far as that fiend
who hurt your brother, I'm-a...

18:45.709 --> 18:47.744
I'm-a take care of that,
a'ight?

18:51.581 --> 18:53.715
Take care of it?

18:53.717 --> 18:54.983
Yeah.

18:54.985 --> 18:56.584
What you gonna do?

18:56.586 --> 18:58.687
- You gonna hurt him, kill him?
- Ny, come on.

18:58.689 --> 19:01.756
No, no, no, no. 'Cause that's
your answer to everything.

19:01.758 --> 19:04.028
Right? That's who you are.

19:05.229 --> 19:07.763
Today, it was two people
we know,

19:07.765 --> 19:09.131
but every day,
it's at least two

19:09.133 --> 19:12.036
who are hurt 'cause of you, D.

19:13.137 --> 19:14.602
I know no other way.

19:14.604 --> 19:15.704
<font face="Rockwell">(SCOFFS)</font> Come on.

19:15.706 --> 19:17.073
I grew up here, too.

19:17.075 --> 19:19.108
We all have to make
choices in life

19:19.110 --> 19:22.677
to heal or to hurt,
and you chose the latter.

19:22.679 --> 19:24.246
- <font face="Rockwell">(SIGHS)</font>
- Don't you care

19:24.248 --> 19:26.582
about this Purge or what it
could do to our community?

19:26.584 --> 19:28.818
I mean...

19:28.820 --> 19:31.687
More selfish bullshit.

19:31.689 --> 19:33.257
Wow.

19:37.228 --> 19:40.029
Now, the Purge is one day.

19:40.031 --> 19:43.666
You, Dmitri,

19:43.668 --> 19:47.105
destroy this community
364 days a year.

19:50.075 --> 19:52.244
You weren't always like this.

19:54.747 --> 19:56.747
The man I knew and loved
years ago

19:56.749 --> 19:58.783
had courage and had soul.

20:01.719 --> 20:03.122
I miss that man.

20:07.725 --> 20:09.760
But thank you for the invite.

20:09.762 --> 20:11.029
I, uh, uh...

20:11.031 --> 20:12.230
We're gonna be fine
without you.

20:12.232 --> 20:13.232
- Oh.
- Uh, um...

20:14.633 --> 20:16.735
Stay the fuck away from us,
Dmitri.

20:19.905 --> 20:21.241
<font face="Rockwell">(DOOR OPENS)</font>

20:22.641 --> 20:24.243
<font face="Rockwell">(DOOR CLOSES)</font>

20:29.281 --> 20:31.682
<font face="Rockwell">WOMAN:</font> <i>And you're angry.</i>

20:31.684 --> 20:32.850
<font face="Rockwell">ISAIAH:</font> Yes.

20:32.852 --> 20:34.152
I'm angry.

20:34.154 --> 20:35.820
Very angry.

20:35.822 --> 20:37.223
You want to release that anger?

20:39.025 --> 20:41.259
I need to.

20:41.261 --> 20:44.395
Thank you for
your honest answers.

20:44.397 --> 20:46.598
First, a few formalities.

20:48.234 --> 20:51.869
Baptisias, the official flower
of the experiment.

20:51.871 --> 20:53.871
They represent rebirth.

20:53.873 --> 20:55.673
In the box,
you have recording lenses.

20:55.675 --> 20:57.142
Contacts.

20:57.144 --> 20:59.777
Should you choose
to actively participate,

20:59.779 --> 21:01.213
wear them on the evening,

21:01.215 --> 21:02.782
and they'll document
everything you do.

21:04.151 --> 21:06.185
As I said,
greater participation

21:06.187 --> 21:08.320
yields greater
financial compensation.

21:08.322 --> 21:11.390
Next, we'll implant
a tracking device.

21:11.392 --> 21:15.127
After that, you'll be all set,
as they say...

21:15.129 --> 21:17.064
to purge.

21:33.080 --> 21:34.179
<font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font> What do you mean,
I can't get off?

21:34.181 --> 21:35.848
<font face="Rockwell">MAN #2:</font>
No, let me through!

21:35.850 --> 21:37.250
- <font face="Rockwell">(HORNS HONKING)</font>
- Turn around. You gotta get out.

21:37.252 --> 21:39.319
- No.
- Let me off this island!

21:39.321 --> 21:41.755
<font face="Rockwell">(HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING)</font>

21:54.001 --> 21:57.035
A lot of people you know
are gonna be there, okay?

21:57.037 --> 21:58.705
Why can't we just stay home?

21:58.707 --> 22:00.773
Selina, because we can't, okay?

22:00.775 --> 22:02.476
This is the safest place
in the neighborhood.

22:02.478 --> 22:05.111
- I'm scared.
- I'm gonna take care of you.

22:05.113 --> 22:06.946
I won't let anything happen,
okay, <i>mamita?</i>

22:06.948 --> 22:08.047
Okay.

22:08.049 --> 22:09.916
- Hey.
- <font face="Rockwell">(CHUCKLING)</font>

22:09.918 --> 22:11.452
- Okay, come on.
- Okay.

22:11.454 --> 22:13.755
<i>Venga, ven.</i>
Let's hurry up.

22:17.759 --> 22:21.962
<font face="Rockwell">(QUIET CHATTER)</font>

22:21.964 --> 22:23.230
- Hey.
- Hey.

22:23.232 --> 22:24.498
Luisa, Selina.

22:24.500 --> 22:26.500
Hey. Oh, I didn't expect
to see you.

22:26.502 --> 22:29.069
I thought you would have left
the island by now.

22:29.071 --> 22:31.405
Oh, I was going to,
but, you know, the money, Nya.

22:31.407 --> 22:32.739
$5,000 to stay?

22:32.741 --> 22:34.241
That's life-changing for us.

22:34.243 --> 22:35.808
- We need it.
- Yeah.

22:35.810 --> 22:38.145
Pastor Almory opened up
the church to everyone.

22:38.147 --> 22:39.812
- Mm-hmm.
- Okay? We got cots.

22:39.814 --> 22:42.250
There's gonna be security
at the door, food.

22:42.252 --> 22:45.052
And Pastor's going to deliver
a sermon later tonight.

22:45.054 --> 22:46.787
<font face="Rockwell">DOLORES:</font>
Oh, Lord, forgive me.

22:46.789 --> 22:48.055
Pastor's a wonderful man,

22:48.057 --> 22:50.024
but his sermons
bore me to death.

22:50.026 --> 22:51.526
It's a goddamn
snooze fest, okay?

22:51.528 --> 22:53.761
- <font face="Rockwell">(LAUGHTER)</font>
- <font face="Rockwell">DOLORES:</font> Yeah.

22:53.763 --> 22:55.129
Why don't you make
yourselves at home?

22:55.131 --> 22:56.431
- Anything you need.
- <font face="Rockwell">ALMORY:</font> You'll be all right.

22:56.433 --> 22:57.965
Thank you for coming.

22:57.967 --> 22:59.266
Thank you so much.

22:59.268 --> 23:00.367
Thank you for coming.

23:00.369 --> 23:02.770
Of course. I appreciate it.

23:02.772 --> 23:04.105
Hey, y'all doing good?

23:04.107 --> 23:06.074
We gonna be all right.

23:06.076 --> 23:08.779
<font face="Rockwell">(CELL PHONE BUZZING)</font>

23:12.249 --> 23:13.848
Sis.

23:13.850 --> 23:15.150
Are you there yet?

23:15.152 --> 23:16.518
I'm-I'm already
in Brooklyn, sis.

23:16.520 --> 23:18.820
A block away from Uncle...
Uncle T's place.

23:18.822 --> 23:21.256
Um, I-I got the last bus
off the island.

23:21.258 --> 23:23.425
<font face="Rockwell">(CHUCKLES)</font>
Yeah, I wish you were with me.

23:23.427 --> 23:24.993
I know. I know.

23:24.995 --> 23:26.963
But I just had to get
as many people

23:26.965 --> 23:29.031
off the street
and into the church as I could.

23:29.033 --> 23:30.099
Stay safe.

23:30.101 --> 23:31.300
I'll be fine.

23:31.302 --> 23:32.903
A'ight.

24:47.614 --> 24:50.113
What you say, Skeletor?

24:50.115 --> 24:51.850
<font face="Rockwell">(GUN CLICKS)</font>

25:03.330 --> 25:05.196
<font face="Rockwell">NEWS ANCHOR:</font>
There are candlelight vigils

25:05.198 --> 25:07.065
happening all over the country.

25:07.067 --> 25:10.034
Now let's go to Anne with
footage from just moments ago.

25:10.036 --> 25:13.237
That is the last of the buses
leaving the island.

25:13.239 --> 25:16.241
The last ferry
left minutes ago.

25:16.243 --> 25:18.009
We're just minutes away now,

25:18.011 --> 25:19.545
and the questions
on everyone's mind

25:19.547 --> 25:21.382
<i>remain the same.</i>

25:22.683 --> 25:24.450
Will people participate?

25:24.452 --> 25:26.217
Will Staten Islanders prove

25:26.219 --> 25:28.454
that this is a night
America needs?

25:28.456 --> 25:30.522
<font face="Rockwell">NEWS ANCHOR #2:</font> Thanks, Anne.
And now we're going

25:30.524 --> 25:32.290
to take you live
to the White House,

25:32.292 --> 25:33.991
where President Bracken
will address

25:33.993 --> 25:36.462
the citizens of Staten Island
and the nation

25:36.464 --> 25:39.699
for the start
of the first experiment.

25:39.701 --> 25:43.369
The courageous citizens
of Staten Island...

25:43.371 --> 25:46.338
those pioneers...
will be part of something

25:46.340 --> 25:49.009
that could bring about
great change.

25:50.344 --> 25:53.147
We are all
Staten Islanders tonight.

25:54.248 --> 25:56.515
Good luck.

