52:36.692 --> 52:37.492
<font face="Rockwell">(NYA WHIMPERS)</font>

52:37.494 --> 52:39.926
<font face="Rockwell">NYA:</font>
Please. Please, no, no, no.

52:39.928 --> 52:41.563
No, no, don't. Please.

52:42.698 --> 52:44.365
<font face="Rockwell">(LAUGHING)</font>

52:44.367 --> 52:47.303
<font face="Rockwell">(LAUGHS HYSTERICALLY)</font>

52:49.071 --> 52:50.238
What the fuck?

52:50.240 --> 52:52.673
