57:30.493 --> 57:33.428
<font face="Rockwell">ANNE:</font> <i>The governor is sending
500 state troopers tomorrow...</i>

57:33.430 --> 57:35.030
Don't question it.

57:35.032 --> 57:36.967
This is a good thing
for both of us.

