Bastards went inside.

58:02.093 --> 58:05.260
About a dozen of them
started shooting at everyone.

58:05.262 --> 58:07.096
We had to pretend we were dead.

58:07.098 --> 58:10.232
We covered ourselves
in somebody else's blood.

58:10.234 --> 58:12.436
I'm so glad you're okay.

58:13.537 --> 58:14.336
D-Dolores. Dolores.

58:14.338 --> 58:16.071
Where's Dolores?
Have you seen her?

58:16.073 --> 58:17.473
We don't know.
