58:21.446 --> 58:23.279
- No, no.
- No.

58:23.281 --> 58:25.115
<font face="Rockwell">LUISA & SELINA:</font>
No!

58:25.117 --> 58:27.283
Some people got out, Nya.

58:27.285 --> 58:29.386
But not everyone.

58:29.388 --> 58:30.988
<font face="Rockwell">ISAIAH:</font>
Nya.

58:32.491 --> 58:34.591
- Her phone's off.
- <font face="Rockwell">(RAPID GUNFIRE NEARBY)</font>

58:34.593 --> 58:36.226
- <font face="Rockwell">(GASPING)</font>
- We can't be out here anymore.

58:36.228 --> 58:37.660
Let's get to my apartment now.

58:37.662 --> 58:39.229
- Okay.
- Come on.

58:39.231 --> 58:40.631
<font face="Rockwell">LUISA:</font>
Be careful.

58:40.633 --> 58:42.901
