58:46.372 --> 58:48.206
<font face="Rockwell">LORENZO:</font>
Check this out.

58:49.575 --> 58:52.108
They all got the same ink.

58:52.110 --> 58:53.143
What is it?

58:53.145 --> 58:54.545
Mercs.

58:54.547 --> 58:57.447
Saw these fuckers overseas
after I enlisted.

58:57.449 --> 58:59.349
They badasses for hire.

58:59.351 --> 59:00.583
They'll work
for anyone anywhere

59:00.585 --> 59:02.288
as long as the cash is correct.

59:03.523 --> 59:05.089
Like Blackwater
back in the days.

59:05.091 --> 59:08.726
Usually ex-military,
and not just American.

59:08.728 --> 59:10.963
These fuckers
are the real deal.

59:16.402 --> 59:18.404
Show me Park and Fourth
ten minutes ago.

59:19.505 --> 59:22.072
<font face="Rockwell">(TYPING)</font>

59:22.074 --> 59:23.275
Here.

59:23.277 --> 59:25.544
<font face="Rockwell">UPDALE:</font>
Follow those trucks backwards.

59:25.546 --> 59:28.780
Use drones, street cams,
whatever you need access to,

59:28.782 --> 59:30.749
to see where the hell
they came from.

59:30.751 --> 59:33.685
<font face="Rockwell">SABIAN:</font> There's purging
going on all over the city.

59:33.687 --> 59:35.387
It's turning.

59:35.389 --> 59:38.055
- I knew it would.
- <font face="Rockwell">MAN:</font> Sir.

59:38.057 --> 59:40.159
We have a breach
inside a private office.

59:43.730 --> 59:45.297
I tracked those trucks
all the way

59:45.299 --> 59:46.531
across the island to here:

59:46.533 --> 59:47.800
a remote area
of abandoned factories.

59:47.802 --> 59:49.635
Watch this now.

59:49.637 --> 59:52.139
At around midnight,
something strange happens.

59:57.377 --> 59:59.177
I did a vehicle search
on all systems,

59:59.179 --> 01:00:01.813
and every one of these vehicles
ended up in Park Hill,

01:00:01.815 --> 01:00:03.315
Mariners Harbor and Stapleton.

01:00:03.317 --> 01:00:04.749
The low-income areas
of the island.

01:00:04.751 --> 01:00:06.551
And they're attacking
crowded places:

01:00:06.553 --> 01:00:09.388
churches, apartment buildings,
Purge parties.

01:00:09.390 --> 01:00:11.257
The gangs know
where people are gathering

01:00:11.259 --> 01:00:12.592
because of
the tracking implants.

